  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "An atmospheric <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">gas</span> found in the hostile conditions of <span class=\"name name-special\">gas giants</span>.<br><br>Methane is readily harvested from equipment deployed on <span class=\"name name-technology\">gas</span> worlds.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "能够在<span class=\"name name-special\">气态巨星</span>的恶劣环境中找到的一种<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>。<br><br>可以通过部署在<span class=\"name name-technology\">气体</span>行星上的装备直接采集甲烷。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-special\">氣態巨行星</span>惡劣條件下可見的大氣<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氣體</span>。<br><br>甲烷可透過部署在<span class=\"name name-technology\">氣體</span>世界的設備輕易採集。"
  },
